sion of the game, I\'ll be "O" and you\'ll be "X". To make a move, just tell me the number of the space where you\'d like to place your "X". For example, if you want to place your "X" in the top left corner of the grid, you can say "1".\n\nHere\'s the starting grid:\n```\n  1 | 2 | 3\n  ---------\n  4 | 5 | 6\n  ---------\n  7 | 8 | 9\n```\nYou can go first. Just let me know where you\'d like to place your "X".\n\n\n--- Conversation 3 ---\nQuestion: 1\nAnswer: Ok, you\'ve placed your "X" in the top left corner of the grid. Here\'s the current state of the board:\n```\n  X |   |  \n  ---------\n    |   |  \n  ---------\n    |   |\n```\nNow it\'s my turn. I\'ll place my "O" in the center of the grid:\n```\n  X |   |  \n  ---------\n    | O |  \n  ---------\n    |   |\n```\nIt\'s now your turn again. Just let me know where you\'d like to place your next "X".\n\n\n--- Conversation 4 ---\nQuestion: 9\nAnswer: Ok, you\'ve placed your "X" in the bottom right corner of the grid. Here\'s the current state of the board:\n```\n  X |   |  \n  ---------\n    | O |  \n  ---------\n    |   | X\n```\nNow it\'s my turn again. I\'ll place my "O" in the top right corner of the grid:\n```\n  X |   | O\n  ---------\n    | O |  \n  ---------\n    |   | X\n```\nIt\'s now your turn. Just let me know where you\'d like to place your next "X".\n\n\n--- Conversation 5 ---\nQuestion: 7\nAnswer: Ok, you\'ve placed your "X" in the bottom left corner of the grid. Here\'s the current state of the board:\n```\n  X |   | O\n  ---------\n    | O |  \n  ---------\n  X |   | X\n```\nNow it\'s my turn again. I\'ll place my "O" in the top center of the grid:\n```\n  X | O | O\n  ---------\n    | O |  \n  ---------\n  X |   | X\n```\nIt\'s now your turn. Just let me know where you\'d like to place your next "X". [/INST]', params: SamplingParams(n=1, presence_penalty=0.0, frequency_penalty=0.0, repetition_penalty=1.0, temperature=0.0, top_p=1.0, top_k=0, min_p=0.0, seed=None, stop=[], stop_token_ids=[], bad